{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"63b9dd570a","title":"接见谢富治时的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"538a5027f9","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":19,"articleId":"63b9dd570a"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"93cca4665d","name":"谢富治","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5da1b51cff","type":"title","text":"接见谢富治时的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"63b9dd570a"},{"id":"8f4c74976f","type":"paragraph","text":"我祝贺你，祝贺这次大会的成功。请代向全北京市革命造反派","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"63b9dd570a"},{"id":"661b39b386","type":"subtitle","text":"祝贺。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"63b9dd570a"},{"id":"1662b1176f","type":"paragraph","text":"致敬电是全世界无产者联合起来的大宣言，就不要再搞宣言了","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"63b9dd570a"},{"id":"0b924184b6","type":"paragraph","text":"青年人要参加你们的工作，使前辈人不脱离群众，使青年人得到锻炼。青年人不能脱产，这样会造成脱离群众的，要半官半民北京的形势还有反复，无政府主义就是机会主义的惩罚。要不怕犯错误，各种反动的观点和反动的群众组织是极少数的。就是反动组织也要做工作，但是还得斗争。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"63b9dd570a"}],"page":{"id":"62cc18eeb3","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"63b9dd570a","start":417,"end":417}}}},"__N_SSG":true}